their differences but each solution has been rejected by the other 
china proposed a one country two systems formula but this 
was rejected by the nationalists who said it would have reduced 
them to the status of a local government 
in turn the nationalists proposed a one country two 
governments formula but this was rejected by beijing which said 
it would have created two chinas 
