fueling this time lenoir said it now appears atlantis has the 
same type of leaks as columbia which means it is a common 
problem more likely caused by contamination than a faulty design 
he said 
columbias new plumbing is from a different batch than the one 
that was removed and the one that leaked on atlantis and fared 
much better in acceptance tests said shuttle director robert 
crippen 
