which several masked warriors ransacked and looted the home of 
veterinarian rejean mongeon 
he said some members of the warriors society took offense after 
moderate mohawks were quoted in the media as denouncing the attack 
on mongeons home 
the militant warriors society has been vying with elected 
native officials for authority within the mohawk community 
on friday mohawks from the kanewake reserve south of montreal 
